Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一切的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说是你救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 因为是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经被你救了几次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 而且我也不认为自己救了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我们可以继续做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴斯帝国的皇帝雷伊雷嘉利亚·巴斯·雷巴斯的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴斯第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通告祖国巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请马上停止这场无意义的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我平安无事还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图谋杀害我的人并非是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是轨道骑士为了侵略地球而策划的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球人是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请马上停止战争 并和地球缔结和平条约
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请为这场不幸画下休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Tharsis！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从库鲁迪欧城那边搬回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不配驾驶这架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah Drive已经停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说库鲁迪欧伯爵已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据月面基地的激光通信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经确定了亚瑟拉姆公主的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月面基地已经在我等同志的管理下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下的声明不会传入任何人的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始将前往敌人的根据地展开决战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使投入扬陆城的全部战力也并不是一件轻易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经报答了你父亲的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以跟随我军一起作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到地球也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星骑士的扬陆城正在下降！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预测降落地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是以这里地球联合总部为中心的半径20km范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙根本就没有讲和的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃地面设施！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员撤到地下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他们会直接降到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争不是应该结束了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人导弹着弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是碉堡克星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.93,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(656,655)}bunker busters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩盘被打穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹体正朝着基地设施下降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sky Carrier出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18个地点中弹 护壁被贯穿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疑似敌人机动部队的振动源正在下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重甲骑兵部队全机紧急出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shire小队 已就位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Falabella小队 已就位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振动源仍在接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距接触还有59秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机 作好战斗准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眷属！歼灭他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人重甲骑兵的袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎击部队损耗率50%
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜查亚瑟拉姆公主殿下的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦发现立刻射杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 这里太危险了 赶紧转移吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明已公开了暗杀的内情 为什么还会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然他们一开始就是以战争为目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀只不过是个借口而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命自始至终都无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下可是巴斯帝国最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么这里会遭到攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没人能阻止轨道骑士的愚蠢行为了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有我能做的事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经补充约70%的弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他们会直接袭击联合总部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是政府机关被消灭 可是连谈判都无法进行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们根本就没打算谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭武力侵略 攻陷后纳为自己的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不会有人谴责 也不用考虑国际法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是工业革命之前的原始而纯粹的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和公主殿下取得联系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有 虽然我呼叫了她的护卫队长 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有舰载机的机组人员在机上待机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好随时出击的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢准尉 Deucalion会出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 可能会直接在这里展开保卫战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 这里是Mustang队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿奈 你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Mustang-22
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟拉姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴斯的兵器全都是由Aldnoah Drive所驱动的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扬陆城也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:09:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要将Aldnoah Drive停止 扬陆城也会失去机能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要启动者的生命活动停止 Aldnoah Drive就会自动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你心跳停止的时候 Deucalion会坠落一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一种方法是 继承了巴斯皇帝血脉的人可以将其强制停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说 你可以将其停止是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我会把你带到敌人的扬陆城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等一下 阿奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你总是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还问！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你每次都一脸淡定地说出乱来的话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经知道谈判无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主的存在就没有政治价值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在战术上是有帮助的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就应该好好利用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正如果战败了 瑟拉姆也只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:09:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合理的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就知道合理！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道这会造成多少伤亡吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这么做也会造成很多伤亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就可以乱来了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为这是战争啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 雪姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得应该在可能性最大的方法上赌一把
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz2.369\pos(758,320)}阿\N奈\N\N加\N油\N哦\N！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去请示一下舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为巴斯的公主 竟然要与巴斯人民为敌…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争并不是巴斯的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切都是逆贼的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我无德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们抓紧时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵来电
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在敌人的地下基地中发现了飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主可能搭乘在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军火速前往该处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！那机体还没补充弹药！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah Drive 出力正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在第四层
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会到达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左舷1号炮塔中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是敌人的步兵部队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有能出击的重甲骑兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都在机架上固定着！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 赶紧放出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能马上出击的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是出口！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Deucalion！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右翼发现敌人步兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调转船体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样迂回 别让敌人上船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion开始掉头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 是公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开舱门 收容她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚瑟拉姆公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在地下干船坞进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.79,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,dry dock
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 发现了目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害怕！不害怕！不害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续向前开 我掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱埃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 来了 来了 来了 来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下！这里！这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德尔丽泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧！赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关闭舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾德尔丽泽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经收容了公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制塔 请求开放闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制塔 这里是Deucalion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1号-4号导弹 准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标主闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已打开发射管 可以发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调头 回到船坞去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我来顶着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来说明作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion避开扬陆城的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先爬升到平流层上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上空执行重甲骑兵的空降作战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了！空降过程中可是没地方可藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成为对空火炮的靶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 先将无人驾驶的重甲骑兵投下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强袭部队主体混进诱饵之中进行下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以登陆扬陆城为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已到达20000米高空 翻转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.98,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,655)}Turn over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投下 稻草人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.58,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,655)}Scarecrow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱饵未必会有效 我们可是连对方的火力都不清楚啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来也没有任何东西是我们所清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陆成功的强袭队负责破坏对空炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他们的反击被削弱的时候 让亚瑟拉姆公主登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞠户上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强袭队的编成就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入第一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 与火星兵器的作战经验最丰富的大概就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空出现了多数机影！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对空战斗 开始迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱饵重甲骑兵中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箔条干扰弹 闪光弹扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.61,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,655)}chaff
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.61,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,655)}flare
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强袭队 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang队长呼叫各机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了因暴风雪导致激光通讯的质量低劣外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扬陆城附近的干扰也会很强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在登陆之前不要依赖于指示 各自展开作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-11 了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-22 了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-33 了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-44 了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下降！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要被打中！不要被打中！不要被打中！…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你越怕越会中招哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹最喜欢胆小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昂首挺胸 子弹反而会避开你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-33！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的橙色为标记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿奈 你太快了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以诱饵为挡箭牌下降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过云层就是目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大限度地下降 然后减速
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标确认！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人重甲骑兵接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-22 已确保登陆地点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目视到Mustang-22 正在向你接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱来哦 阿奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能将对空火炮破坏的话 后续部队也会比较轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你的意思是为了帮助我们吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 通信状态异常地清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉没有头等舱 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制台呼叫Princess-1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下降位置待机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 Princess-1开始前往下降位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么都一定要保护好乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你死了也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Princess-1 下降准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Princess-1 下降准备结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Princess-1 下降！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Princess-1 下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:19:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…明明雷达上没有任何反应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对空战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好Deucalion！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使从那架机体中将Aldnoah移植出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为沃雷茵死了 所以无法发挥机能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来由亚瑟拉姆公主殿下再启动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是艘可恨的船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-44！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告损伤情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右舷反重力装置2号-7号停止…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在下坠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将所有能量集中在推力引擎上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标 扬陆城…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这艘船直接冲进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟拉姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有任何信号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢中尉！3点钟方向！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.97,title,NTP,0,0,0,,“新西伯利亚攻防战”
